	<h1 class="title">对更多提名者来说，奥斯卡可能是一个温柔陷阱</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
				<span class="name">Brooks Barnes</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-12-29 10:58:57 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/4783/medium/4783.jpg?1436652980" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


